name: Moon Bay
public_notice: The creator of the contract has the ability to make changes to the smart contract associated with the asset mentioned, such as disabling selling, adjusting fees, creating new tokens, or transferring tokens. Please DYOR before proceed.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
$BAY Token is the ecosystem currency of TSD x Moonmasters. 

What makes your project unique?
With one of the strongest communities on Fantom Network, $BAY Token will bridge the gap between Art and Defi by utilizing the relationships that have been built over the last year+.

History of your project.
TrippySteve's Dao is an Umbrella Organization that Web3 Investors, Artists, and Developers can utilize to build or improve upon their project, skills, or own social environment. 'TSD' was founded by TrippySteve, a crypto investor and Nft collector. 'TSD' is governed by the Moon Master DAO cards. This group has made many important relationships throughout the Fantom Network space and is always looking to grow. MoonMasters Nft are membership to our community. $BAY is our ecosystem currency.

What’s next for your project?
MoonBay Claims on website

What can your token be used for?
It will be used in Live Auctions, Moon Bay Marketplace, Events, and most importantly Defi.

TrippySteve's Dao is an Umbrella Organization that Web3 Investors, Artists, and Developers can utilize to build or improve upon their project, skills, or own social environment. 'TSD' was founded by TrippySteve, a crypto investor and Nft collector. 'TSD' is governed by the Moon Master DAO cards. This group has made many important relationships throughout the Fantom Network space and is always looking to grow. MoonMasters Nft are membership to our community. $BAY is our ecosystem currency.

What’s next for your project?
MoonBay Claims on website

What can your token be used for?
It will be used in Live Auctions, Moon Bay Marketplace, Events, and most importantly Defi.
